ad_creative_body: Amoureuse des animaux, agricultrice à ses heures et Yamachichoise, découvrez de plus près Ruth Ellen Brosseau députée Canada’s NDP / Le NPD du Canada dans Berthier-Maskinongé. 🌾
ad_creative_link_description: Parachutée et élue en 2011 comme députée dans Berthier-Maskinongé, une circonscription dont elle ne connaissait rien, Ruth Ellen Brosseau y est aujourd’hui chez elle. Peu importe l’issue du scrutin le 21 octobre, elle n’a pas l’intention de partir. Son coeur est désormais à Yamachiche...

For too long, governments in Ottawa have made life easier for the multi-millionaires and mega-corporations, at your expense.

Check out our new ad!🔽

ad_creative_body:
Imagine a government that actually works for you – instead of protecting the interests of the rich and powerful. 

That’s what Jagmeet Singh and the NDP are fighting for – a New Deal for People that will make life easier for you and your family. Learn more and add your name to our critical campaign.
ad_creative_link_description: Learn more and add your name.

Too many Canadians are struggling to afford a place to call home – and yet Liberal and Conservative governments have spent decades making it easier for the rich to get ahead & harder for everyone else.

Jagmeet Singh and the NDP are fighting to make things easier for you, with a plan to fix the housing crisis. Learn more and add your name to our campaign.

ad_creative_link_title: We Will Fix the Housing Crisis

ad_creative_body:
The Trudeau Liberals campaigned on a housing plan, but have wasted time and held back funding for years instead of fixing the crisis.

Jagmeet Singh and the NDP have a plan for immediate action to bring relief to families, and help Canadians find a safe, affordable place to call home.
ad_creative_link_description: Learn more and add your name.
ad_creative_link_title: We Will Fix the Housing Crisis

ad_creative_body:
Too many Canadians are stuck in housing that’s too expensive or doesn’t fit their needs, but they feel like they have nowhere to go. 

The Liberal government doesn’t understand that
we’re in a housing crisis.

We’ve got a plan to create half a million units of quality,
affordable housing across the country. Add your name and support our plan!
ad_creative_link_description: People can’t afford to wait until 2020 to have an affordable, safe place to live. We need action on housing now - including a plan to add half a million new units of affordable housing. Add your name to support our call.
ad_creative_link_title: URGENT: Canadians need affordable housing now
